config.script:
# Get selected parameters
	selected_params_raw = self.view.custom.selectedValue
	selected_params = list(selected_params_raw)
	
	# Get full dataset from Named Query
	raw_data = self.view.custom.queryData
	
	# Convert dataset to Python format
	py_data = system.dataset.toPyDataSet(raw_data)
	
	# Ensure selected_params is a list
	if isinstance(selected_params, str):
	    selected_params = [selected_params]
	elif selected_params is None:
	    selected_params = []
	
	# Prepare filtered dataset
	headers = ["DateTime"] + selected_params
	filtered_rows = []
	
	for row in py_data:
	    new_row = [row["DateTime"]]
	    for param in selected_params:
	        new_row.append(row[param])
	    filtered_rows.append(new_row)
	
	# Convert back to dataset
	filtered_dataset = system.dataset.toDataSet(headers, filtered_rows)
	
	# Store it in a custom property for chart binding
	self.view.custom.filteredChartData = filtered_dataset
